description.narrative: The Project Development Objectives (PDO) are to: (a) improve the reliability and efficiency of the irrigation and drainage services and strengthen market linkages for irrigated products in selected irrigation schemes; and (b) improve availability of equipment and supplies for COVID-19 response.
